General.Name: K2FLY Ltd
General.Description: K2fly Limited provides enterprise-level technical assurance and reporting solutions in the areas of environmental, social, and governance functions in Australia. It provides digital transformation and implantation services comprising procurement services; implement, optimise, upgrade, and support solutions; program/project management; architecture and business analysis solution; and integration services, such as change management, testing, rollout, and support services, as well as sells own and third party solutions; and offers asset management consultancy services primarily to utility sector. The company also offers heritage management, land access, ground disturbance, tailing management, mine rehabilitation, resources reporting, model manager, ore blocker, and mine geology solutions. K2fly Limited was incorporated in 2007 and is headquartered in Subiaco, Australia.
